snippet: At least 83 people have been killed in recent days in floods and landslides in three different parts of China, according to reports.
abstract: At least 83 people have been killed in floods and landslides in three different parts of China, as result of heavy rains.

headline.main: Dozens Dead After Heavy Rains in China
